lead_paragraph: Zach Randolph scored 25 points and grabbed four rebounds in the final minute to lead the Memphis Grizzlies past the Utah Jazz 94-88 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Randolph Scores 25 to Lead Grizzlies Past Jazz 94-88
